VO_OSMP_SRC_ADAPTIVE_STREAMING_INFO_EVENT_CHUNK_BEGINDOWNLOAD

public static final VOCommonPlayerListener.VO_OSMP_SRC_ADAPTIVE_STREAMING_INFO_EVENT VO_OSMP_SRC_ADAPTIVE_STREAMING_INFO_EVENT_CHUNK_BEGINDOWNLOAD
Chunk download begin. VO_OSMPListener callback param obj will be VOOSMPChunkInfo. If the return value of this callback is VOOSMPType.VO_OSMP_RETURN_CODE.VO_OSMP_SRC_ERR_CHUNK_SKIP, source must drop this chunk; This event is synced with callback by onRequestListener, you should return a value
